To be able to run SeriChat you just have to run the JAR-file (SeriChat.jar) through the terminal with the below mentioned steps (it is tested on Linux and Mac OSX).
For each step you have to open a new terminal window and navigate to the folder where SeriChat.jar is located.


1- Create the bootstrapping node 
java -jar SeriChat.jar


2- Create a group 
add groupowners name, -c (for create) , name of group, and passwordjava -jar SeriChat.jar Niels -c AU 123456

3- Join a group
add a name for new member, -j (for join), name of group, and password
java -jar SeriChat.jar Bilal -j AU 123456


Step 2 and step 3 can be repeated for creating new groups and adding new group members.